paragraphs:
We fine-tuned the Llama3.1-8B model with full parameters fine-tuning on 32 (2*16) 64G AMD INSTINCT MI250X GPUs. The distributed training was run with the DeepSpeed (Rasley et al., 2020) framework with ZeRO stage 2. The learning rate is 5e-6. We use AdamW (Loshchilov and Hutter, 2019) as the optimizer with β1=0.9 eta_{1}=0.9 and β2=0.999 eta_{2}=0.999. The template for the training sequence is: "Based on the following passages, answer the question.

<passages>
{body}

</passages>

 Question: {question}
Answer: {answer}". The default EOS token is ’</s>’.
